tweet: El número de nuevos casos de COVID-19 entre residentes del Condado de Boulder de 0 a 11 años está bajando.  Casi 23,500 niños de 5 a 11 años viven en el  condado y son elegibles para vacunarse.  Proveedores de la vacuna contra COVID-19:  https://t.co/l6zXRJNgUM  https://t.co/2M5MIYfN59

name: Bo Co Public Health
tweet: New COVID-19 cases among Boulder County residents between the ages of 0-11 have been declining.  There are roughly 23,500 children between 5-11 in Boulder County who are eligible to be vaccinated.  A list of providers and clinics is available at  https://t.co/Ipcce2ue88.  https://t.co/NYMr0HHtDN

name: Bo Co Public Health
tweet: El Condado de Boulder está experimentando un aumento en los casos de COVID-19 debido a la #VarianteDelta e influenza. Se predice que los casos continuarán aumentando a medida que las personas se reúnan adentro durante las vacaciones.  Lee más:  https://t.co/9obwsUyNhN  https://t.co/m9fBOQE3dy

name: Bo Co Public Health
tweet: Boulder County is experiencing a surge in cases of both the COVID-19 #DeltaVariant and influenza. Current modeling predicts cases will continue to grow, particularly as people come together for the holidays and gather indoors. Read the press release:  https://t.co/ETLZTSFzHb  https://t.co/XqReejUQb8
